                Aia <expan><abbr>Prim</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> X <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ita</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ater</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">et</supplied> <lb n="3"/>Casata Magi<lb break="no" n="4"/>ona <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan> <abbr>m</abbr>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die vorgezeicheten Hilfslinien wurden weitgehend ignoriert. S in Form eines Blitzes . Z. 4: p(osuit) m(emoriam), m(emoria), m(emoriae), M(anibus)? &amp;apos;Casata Magiona&amp;apos; könnte auch für &amp;apos;Casata Magionis filia&amp;apos; stehen. (B): Hild: Z. 4: D(is) M(anibus).</p>
            </div>
